author: GameSpot
description:
Drop into skate.™ Season 1 and let the good times roll! Explore skate spots, push your limits, and create in this dynamic social world that’s alive with energy. Complete weekly Challenges and keep stacking rewards to skate in style. Plus, discover fresh places to ride in evolving Community Parks. There’s also new music, more branded gear, and the first skate.Pass*.

Play free** now on PlayStation® 4, PlayStation® 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, and PC via EA App, Epic Games Store and Steam.

*Skate.Pass content requires Season 1 skate.Pass (standard track available in-game; premium track requires in-game purchase) & gameplay to unlock. Skate (available separately) & all game updates required.

**Applicable platform account and platform subscription (sold separately) may be required. Persistent internet connection and EA account required. Age restrictions apply. Includes optional in-game purchases.
title: skate. | Early Access Season 1 Overview Trailer
